channel.title: My Botting Thread - Runescape Account
channel.description:
[center]Hello Moparscapians,
Today, I'm making a topic of my account that i'm botting. Of-Course i'll be blocking out the name in case Jagex is lurking around. My goal is to get 95 Woodcutting. Then i'm going to get 95 Fire, The 95 Mining then i'm going to get 99 Fishing.
Then i'll make good amounts of cash and trade it to my main and keep doing so, I'll keep you guys updated of my botting account and i'll show you My proggies every couple of hours (12 Hours). I'll post my proggie under all this text. I'll have an update goal thing underneath the picture.
Here is my pictures; Please keep in mind this account is only 2 days and 10 Hours old. Been botting a lot.
[IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2ih4k5g.png[/img] [sup]81 Woodcutting - Updated 28/01/2011[/sup] [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/168uzrm.png[/img] [sup]84 Woodcutting - Updated 29/01/2011[/sup]
Thanks, I hope you check back and look at this. [/center]
